1. Ja sam juče *zaradio* puno novca na poslu. (I earned a lot of money at work yesterday.)
2. On je *zaradio* veliku nagradu za svoj rad. (He earned a big reward for his work.)
3. *Zaradila* je nekoliko ožiljaka na putu do vrha planine. (She earned a few scars on the way to the mountain top.)
4. Ti ćeš *zaraditi* kaznu ako nastaviš da kršiš pravila. (You will earn a punishment if you continue to break the rules.)
5. Ovaj posao će ti *zaraditi* mnogo novca. (This job will earn you a lot of money.)
6. Oni su *zaradili* svoj odmor i sada mogu da se opuste. (They earned their vacation and can now relax.)
7. Kako si *zaradio* taj ožiljak? (How did you earn that scar?)
8. Nadam se da ćeš *zaraditi* dovoljno novca za putovanje. (I hope you will earn enough money for the trip.)
9. Ovaj film je *zaradio* mnogo novca na blagajni. (This movie earned a lot of money at the box office.)
10. *Zaradili* su pohvale za svoj trud i rad na projektu. (They earned praise for their effort and work on the project.)